it does, you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer high-level questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"615d472c-c97a-4ae5-b05a-bc419b94b27f","uuid":"2960fcf1-61f2-45b5-8435-161e83862515"}
